In [202]:
def format_popup(tree):
    link, name, sci_name, points, img, county, state = tree['link'], tree['name'], tree['sci_name'], tree['points'], tree['img'], tree['county'], tree['state']
    return f'<b><a href = "{link}" target = "_blank"> {name} </a></b><br><i>{sci_name}</i><br>Points: {points}<br> County: {county}, {state} <img src = {img}></img>'
In [208]:
m = folium.Map(location=[39.833, -98.583333], zoom_start = 4, tiles = 'Stamen Terrain')

states = set(trees['state'])
state_clusters = {state: folium.plugins.MarkerCluster(name = state) for state in states}

for cluster in state_clusters.values():
    cluster.add_to(m)
    
for index, tree in trees.iterrows():
    try:
        folium.Marker(
            location = [tree['lat'], tree['long']], 
            popup = format_popup(tree),
            icon = folium.features.CustomIcon(tree['img']
                                     , icon_size = (18 * tree['qtile'] ** (1/3),18 * tree['qtile'] ** (1/3))),
        ).add_to(state_clusters[tree['state']])
    except:
        print(tree['name'], tree['county'], tree['state'])
